Package com.i2group.apollo.searchservice.transport

Contains classes for the services that search for items in the Analysis Repository and external data sources.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
CardInfo Information about a Card in an ItemSearchResult that has the Propertys with the values matched by a search operation.
DumbbellInfo Information about a dumbbell result ultimately referred to by an ItemSearchResult.
DuplicateItems Items that are considered to be duplicates because they all match a particular ItemDiscriminator.
Excerpt An excerpt of a Property value that includes the text matched by a search.
FilterInfo Information about how Items are to be processed during a filter operation.
FilterInfoList A container for FilterInfos.
IndexSnapshotInfo Information about a snapshot that has been taken of the search index.
ItemDiscriminator A means of characterizing an Item that is used for determining whether other Items of the same ItemType are duplicates.
ItemInfo Information about the Item ultimately referred to by an ItemSearchResult.
ItemScopeFilter A ScopeFilter that restricts the scope of a search for a SearchNode to specific Items.
ItemSearchResult A score and a ResultInfo that together make up a single search result.
ItemTypeCount Information about the number of Items of a particular ItemType, and (optionally) at a particular location in a dumbbell.
ItemTypeIdList A container for ItemType identifiers that must contain at least one entry.
LinkInfo Information about the content and orientation of a Link that is ultimately referred to by an ItemSearchResult.
PagedExpandResults Contains the SearchExpandResults and PageResultInfo that form one page of the results of expanding one or more seeds.
PageInfo Information about a page of results to be retrieved from a service.
PageResultInfo Information about a page of results returned from a service.
PropertyGroupInfo Information about a PropertyGroup in a Card that has the Propertys with the values matched by a search operation.
PropertyInfo Information about a Property with a value that was matched by a search operation.
ResultInfo Information about the result ultimately referred to by an ItemSearchResult.
ScopeFilter A description of the scope within which the search for a SearchNode should take place.
SearchExpandResults Contains the SearchExpansionMaps and the Items that form the results of expanding from one or more seeds.
SearchExpansionMap Contains the ItemIdentifier of the seed Entity in an expand, and the ItemIdentifiers of the Links connected to that seed.
SearchNode A set of criteria that an Entity or a Link must match in order to be returned by a dumbbell or network search.
SearchResults Contains the Items and ItemSearchResults that form the results of a search operation.
SearchSummary A summary of the results of a search or dumbbell search operation.
SetInfo Information about how the set and its contents are specified.
SetScopeFilter A ScopeFilter that restricts the scope of a search for a SearchNode to a specific set.
SortInfo Information about how Items are to be processed during a sort operation.
TextRange A description of part of the String in an Excerpt.
 

Enum Summary
DumbbellPart Indicates the part of a dumbbell to which a particular operation or result applies.
DumbbellResultOrientation Indicates the orientation of a dumbbell result with respect to the orientation specified in the search request.
FilterBasis Indicates what aspect of Items will be used as the basis for a filter operation.
FilterOperator Indicates the type of comparison to be performed in a filter operation.
PageSelection Indicates which page of results to retrieve from a search operation.
SetSelectionBasis Indicates how the set and its contents will be retrieved.
SortBasis Indicates what aspect of Items is used as the basis for a sort operation.
SortDirection Indicates the direction in which to perform a sort operation.
SortType Indicates what aspect of Items is used as the basis for a sort operation.
TextRangeType Indicates whether a TextRange describes a match or an ellipsis.
 

Package com.i2group.apollo.searchservice.transport Description

Contains classes for the services that search for items in the Analysis Repository and external data sources.
